%sh
export VM_LOCAL_PATH=/root/project
export HADOOP_PATH=/user/root/project
export DATASET_FILE=crime_rate_ds.csv

# sudo mkdir $VM_LOCAL_PATH

# hadoop fs -mkdir $HADOOP_PATH    
# hadoop fs -put $VM_LOCAL_PATH/$DATASET_FILE $HADOOP_PATH

hadoop fs -ls $HADOOP_PATH

%md

## Create external table

%sql
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS crime_rate_ext

%sql

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE crime_rate_ext (
    id	INT	,
    EVENT_UNIQUE_ID	STRING	,
    REPORT_DATE	STRING	,
    OCC_DATE	STRING	,
    REPORT_YEAR	INT	,
    REPORT_MONTH	STRING	,
    REPORT_DAY	INT	,
    REPORT_DOY	INT	,
    REPORT_DOW	STRING	,
    REPORT_HOUR	INT	,
    OCC_YEAR	INT	,
    OCC_MONTH	STRING	,
    OCC_DAY	INT	,
    OCC_DOY	INT	,
    OCC_DOW	STRING	,
    OCC_HOUR	INT	,
    DIVISION	STRING	,
    LOCATION_TYPE	STRING	,
    PREMISES_TYPE	STRING	,
    UCR_CODE	INT	,
    UCR_EXT	INT	,
    OFFENCE	STRING	,
    MCI_CATEGORY	STRING	,
    HOOD_158	STRING	,
    NEIGHBOURHOOD_158	STRING	,
    HOOD_140	STRING	,
    NEIGHBOURHOOD_140	STRING
)
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED
FIELDS TERMINATED BY ','
STORED AS TEXTFILE
LOCATION '/user/root/project'

%sql

SELECT * FROM crime_rate_ext
distribute by rand()
sort by rand()
limit 100

CREATE TABLE cleaned_crime AS
SELECT *
FROM crime_rate_orc
WHERE NOT (
    EVENT_UNIQUE_ID IS NULL OR
    REPORT_DATE IS NULL OR
    OCC_DATE IS NULL OR
    REPORT_YEAR IS NULL OR
    REPORT_MONTH IS NULL OR
    REPORT_DAY IS NULL OR
    REPORT_DOY IS NULL OR
    REPORT_DOW IS NULL OR
    REPORT_HOUR IS NULL OR
    OCC_YEAR IS NULL OR
    OCC_MONTH IS NULL OR
    OCC_DAY IS NULL OR
    OCC_DOY IS NULL OR
    OCC_DOW IS NULL OR
    OCC_HOUR IS NULL OR
    DIVISION IS NULL OR
    LOCATION_TYPE IS NULL OR
    PREMISES_TYPE IS NULL OR
    UCR_CODE IS NULL OR
    UCR_EXT IS NULL OR
    OFFENCE IS NULL OR
    MCI_CATEGORY IS NULL OR
    HOOD_158 IS NULL OR
    NEIGHBOURHOOD_158 IS NULL OR
    HOOD_140 IS NULL OR
    NEIGHBOURHOOD_140 IS NULL
)

%md
Finding the year in which crime data was the highest

msg.data: Finding the year in which crime data was the highest

paragraphs.text:
%sql
SELECT Report_Year, COUNT(*) AS Year_Count
FROM cleaned_crime
GROUP BY Report_Year
ORDER BY Year_Count DESC

    OCC_YEAR,
    COUNT(*) AS crime_count
FROM
    cleaned_crime
WHERE
    NEIGHBOURHOOD_158 = "West Humber-Clairville"
GROUP BY
    OCC_YEAR
ORDER BY
    OCC_YEAR

%sql
SELECT
    OCC_YEAR,
    OCC_MONTH,
    MAX(case_count) AS highest_cases
FROM (
    SELECT
        OCC_YEAR,
        OCC_MONTH,
        COUNT(*) AS case_count
    FROM cleaned_crime
    GROUP BY OCC_YEAR, OCC_MONTH
) AS monthly_cases
GROUP BY OCC_YEAR, OCC_MONTH
ORDER BY OCC_YEAR Desc

        WHEN 'July' THEN 7
